2024 Annual Picnic

Join us for the annual Gusinje Foundation Picnic! There will be a number of sporting events, kids activities, live music, food, and more! We’re looking forward to spending the day together!

What do we do?

Programs

The Gusinje Foundation provides assistance for the rapid development of infrastructure and utilities in the native region.

Donations

The organization accepts donations to support its programs and initiatives.

Cultural heritage

The Gusinje Foundation works to preserve and promote the cultural heritage of the region.
